<div class="relative w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-20">

  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <nav class="flex mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li>
          <a class="class: hover:text-gray-900" href="/">Home</a>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mx-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Get Involved</span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-2xl font-light">Ready to make a difference? Choose your path!</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mt-2">We have two amazing ways for you to get involved with DPI</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24">
      <div 
    class="relative h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl"
    onclick="scrollToSection('mentor-section')"
  >
        <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_1.jpg", 
        class: "w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110", 
        alt: "DPI Mentor" %>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/30 to-black/70 transition-opacity duration-300">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 w-full">
            <p class="text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Get involved by</p>
            <h3 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Becoming a DPI Mentor</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm">Guide the next generation of tech talent</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div 
    class="relative h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl"
    onclick="scrollToSection('riverside-section')"
  >
        <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_2.jpg", 
        class: "w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110", 
        alt: "Riverside Chat" %>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/30 to-black/70 transition-opacity duration-300">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 w-full">
            <p class="text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Get involved by</p>
            <h3 class="text-white text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Joining our Riverside Chat</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm">Share your journey and inspire others</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="mentor-section" class="mb-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-base font-medium text-left">Give Back By</p>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-left mb-8">Becoming A DPI Mentor</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
        <span class="font-bold">Discovery Partners Institute</span> (DPI) is training the next generation of Illinois's tech talent, 
        and we'd love to have your help. Our enthusiastic trainees are eager for positions where they can grow into 
        valuable leaders and community members, and they need someone like you to guide them on their journeys.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-8 gap-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-24">
    <div class="col-span-3 row-span-2 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[320px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_1.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Mentor" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-5 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[150px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_2.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Program" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-2 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[150px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_3.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Initiative" %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-span-3 bg-gray-300 rounded-md min-h-[150px]">
      <%= image_tag "sample_img/about_dpi_4.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-md", alt: "DPI Community" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-24 px-4">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold italic mb-6">We're looking for leaders with</h3>
    <div class="text-lg font-light">
      <p>At Least Four Years Of Experience In Their Field</p>
      <p>Preferably A Background In Tech, Design, Or Business</p>
      <p>The Ability To Meet At Least Once Every Two Weeks</p>
      <p>The Ability To Attend At Least Six 30-Minute Meetings</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-32 px-4">
    <div class="ml-auto w-1/2">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <span class="font-bold">DPI mentorship is a great way to connect with our diverse talent from all walks of life.</span>
        You'll be guiding one or more Chicagoans through the unspoken rules of the business world and helping them find their footing in an ever-changing job market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-32 px-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">We place our trainees in various fields</h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-16">Sales, Customer Success, Software Development, Project Management</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-16 justify-center items-center">
      <%= image_tag "companies/uls.svg", class: "h-12 grayscale opacity-70", alt: "UL Solutions" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/sap.svg", class: "h-12 grayscale opacity-70", alt: "SAP" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/cibc.svg", class: "h-12 grayscale opacity-70", alt: "CIBC" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/united.svg", class: "h-12 grayscale opacity-70", alt: "United" %>
      <%= image_tag "companies/hcsc.svg", class: "h-12 grayscale opacity-70", alt: "HCSC" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="riverside-section" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-left mb-24 px-4 mt-32">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-xl font-light leading-normal">
        Would you like to explore an
        alternative way to contribute? <br>
        <span class="font-bold underline">Join us for a Riverside chat!</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-24 px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-black mb-8">What is a<br>
          Riverside</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg">
            <span class="italic">Get to know the DPI team</span> and hear from our
            talent network by joining us for a Riverside Chat! This is a casual question-and-answer
            session where our staff will explore your background and the "whys" behind your success.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg">
            <span class="italic">Riverside Chats</span> present a unique opportunity to meet our
            trainees and answer their insightful questions about your field of work. We've had
            cutting-edge leaders from companies like Salesforce, Capital One, and ShipBob join us for Riversides.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg">
            Along with the trainees, we'll discuss how DPI can
            <span class="italic">boost your business</span> through our Tech Accelerator.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="h-full">
        <%= image_tag "sample_img/riverside_chat.jpeg", 
            class: "w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg", 
            alt: "Riverside Chat Session" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mb-32 px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-11 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-black">Make An Impact Today!</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="text-lg space-y-6">
        <p>
          Whether it's through mentorship or just a few hours at a Riverside Chat,
          you can permanently change the future of technology in Illinois. This small
          commitment can make a difference in someone's life and career trajectory.
        </p>
        <p>
          We appreciate your interest in spending time with DPI. If you'd like to
          learn more, please send an email and we'll be in touch soon.
        </p>
        <%= link_to "Contact DPI", "mailto:info@dpi.dev", class: "inline-block bg-black text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  function scrollToSection(sectionId) {
    const element = document.getElementById(sectionId);
    if (element) {
      element.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
    }
  }
</script>